304 Meserole st., Brooklyn, N.Y. 11206 718-599-0464 1-877-848-Lock (5625) Fax 718-360-4853

Empire Lock offers full locksmith services 24/7 in Brooklyn and N.Y. tri-state area. We are transponder specialist (keys with computer chip). Licensed Locksmith. Lost your car keys? We can make your keys thru your vin number with proper documents (registration &license). Se habla espanol

  • Lock-out specialist: cars, trucks, home, apartments
  • Repair locks, cylinders, car cylinders mastered to your keys
  • Custom made keys for locks, Padlocks, Key copies
  • Commercial Locksmith
  • High Security Locks: Mul-T-Locks, Medeco, Kaba Locks, MT5
  • CCTV security surveillance cameras installation
  • Intercom System installed and repair
  • Safe Deposit fire proof & water proof, Safe combination & repairs
  • J bars, cylinder/locks protectors, Door viewer, Panic bars
  • TRANSPONDER KEY KEY SPECIALIST- Key with chip
  • Car keys, Remote key head, Car remotes
  • Car alarm with starter installation
  • Car ignition and car door locks keyed up.
  • Car ignitions repair and sales
  • Keys made for locks, trunks, glove compartment
  • Door knobs, mortise, deadbolts, vestibule, passage, entry
  • Mail box installation, Mail box locks
